#### FAQs

- **How often should a website be redesigned?** Every 3–5 years, or whenever your branding or business direction changes significantly.
- **Can you update my current website?** Yes — but if it's really outdated or built on a bad foundation, a fresh build is usually better.
- **How much does a new website cost?** Our starter sites begin at £400. We can quote based on your goals and features needed.

